pt_run <- as.data.frame(sim24_table) %>% 
    mutate(time = round(time, 0)) %>% 
    filter(time == 1200) %>% 
    filter(!str_detect(species, '__|bound|ecoli|promoter')) %>% 
    mutate(species = factor(species, c("gene_A", "gene_A*", "gene_B",
                                           "gene_K", "gene_C", "gene_D",
                                           "gene_E", "gene_J", "gene_F",
                                           "gene_G", "gene_H"),
                                     c("A", "A*", "B", "K",
                                           "C", "D", "E", "J",
